reviewText: There is only one episode per season on there. This season is incomplete. Where are the rest of the episodes? There are supposed to be a whole season of What Not to Wear.

the gods must not have wanted us to see this episode (I believe it was Clinton's first appearance on WNTW); three disks in a row were defective and would not play. Finally gave up. Other discs in this series have been just fine; a bad pressing (or however they make these things)? Customer service was impeccable; no problem there.
